import Link from 'next/link'
import {Button} from 'antd'

export default ({ children })=>(
    <>
<header> 
    <Link href = '/a?id=1' as= '/a/1' title='aaa'>
        <Button>A</Button>
    </Link>
    <Link href = '/test/b'>
        <Button>B</Button>
    </Link>
</header>
{children}
</>
)
